description:
A free batch photo/image resizer tool

Fotosizer is a free batch photo/image resizer tool. It lets you resize hundreds of photos in a matter of minutes in a quick and easy way.
- Improved sort performance in image selection list.
- Updated libwebp to version 1.5.0 (addressing CVE-2023-4863).
- Fixed error in theme handling when on Windows versions below Windows 10.
